{
  "texts": [
    "The proposed X-Nav framework consists of two stages: 1) Expert Policy Learning, and 2) General Policy Distillation.",
    "In Stage 1, multiple expert policies are trained on randomly generated robot embodiments using DRL with privileged observations.",
    "In Stage 2, the knowledge of expert policies is distilled into a single general policy using IL.",
    "Fig. 4.Fig.",
    "5.45The obstacles used for expert policy learning."
  ]
}